Thanks to [Alana Goyal](https://basecase.vc/blog/unpacking-mcp) for spending a lot of her weekend on Slack with Shane helping us debug subtle differences in how different MCP clients implement the protocol.

## What's next

Some follow-up work we're working on:

- Hosted MCP servers in Mastra Cloud without publishing to NPM
- Enhanced compatibility across all MCP clients
- Better debugging tools for MCP server development
- Support for the [Streamable HTTP MCP transport](https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/modelcontextprotocol/pull/206)

